---
import { Mail, Phone } from '@lucide/astro';
import AnimatedTitle from './AnimatedTitle';

---

<div id="content">
  <main>
    <h1>
      <span class="title-text"><AnimatedTitle client:load /></span>
      <div class="gradient-blur" aria-hidden="true">
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
      </div>
    </h1>
    <p class="intro-text">
      Hey! I'm Liam, a software engineer working in London. I love to create
      beautiful and intuitive interfaces. If you like my work please get in
      touch!
    </p>

    <section id="buttons">
      <a
        href="https://cal.com/liam-piesley-iof3ud"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"><Phone class="icon" />Call</a
      >
      <a href="mailto:liampiesley@gmail.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        ><Mail class="icon" />Email</a
      >
    </section>
    <section id="software">
      <h2>Software Sidequests</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://liamp.uk/gallery-quest">Gallery Quest</a> → Art Nouveau
          card collecting game, exploring HDR and complex CSS animations.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://liamp.uk/timescale">Geologic Timescale</a> → Building a
          more intuitive way to explore Earth's history.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://liamp.uk/chess">Chess Board</a> → A chess app that can
          be played like a real board by placing the phone between two players.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://liamp.uk/minikeys">Minikeys</a> → A tiny Javascript Library
          that plays the piano.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://liamp.uk/aero">Aero</a> → An HDR view from an aeroplane
          window.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://liamp.uk/2048">2048</a> → A clone of the popular 2048 game.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="hardware">
      <h2>Hardware Doodads</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://liamp.uk/lockin">Locked In</a>
          → A hardware switch for disabling social media.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/liampuk/esp-2048">2048 Gamepad</a>
          → A handheld 2048 game based on an esp32. (Work in progress)
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/liampuk/cpu-emu">TTL CPU</a>
          → Designing and building a CPU from scratch with TTL chips. (Work in progress)
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="garden">
      <h2>Website Garden</h2>
      <p>
        Over the years I've grown a collection of well designed websites. From
        unique experiences full of eye catching animation to simple intuitive
        layouts, find some inspiration here:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://webgarden.liamp.uk">Explore the Garden</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="blog">
      <h2>Blog</h2>
      <p>
        I've recently started writing about programming and other things, read
        some articles here:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Latest article →
          <a href="">Minolta Weathermatic Review</a>
          → coming soon
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="about">
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <p>
        I started my career at Nissan in Newcastle while working on my computer
        science degree. After a summer internship at Amazon I moved down to
        London and joined Marshmallow, which I helped grow from a 60 person
        startup to a 500+ employee unicorn. I'm currently building a video
        editor for the web at Blackbird Video.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          See more projects on
          <a href="https://github.com/liampuk" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          Connect on
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/liampuk/" target="_blank"
            >Linkedin</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          Find my
          <a href="https://liamp.uk/liam-piesley-cv.pdf" target="_blank"
            >full CV here</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    #content {
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
      font-family:
        Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Arial Nova', 'Nimbus Sans', Arial,
        sans-serif;
    }

    main {
      padding: 64px;
      max-width: 500px;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 15px;
      padding-bottom: 192px;

      @media (orientation: portrait) {
        padding: 42px;
      }
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      margin-top: 48px;
      font-size: 64px;
      color: #222;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-family: 'Editorial Old', serif;
      font-variant-ligatures: discretionary-ligatures;
      position: sticky;
      top: 32px;
      z-index: 10;
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      width: max-content;
      padding-right: 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      isolation: isolate;

      @media (orientation: portrait) {
        top: 24px;
        font-size: 50px;
        padding-left: 0;
        text-align: center;
        margin-inline: auto;
      }
    }

    .title-text {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 9;
    }

    h1 .title-mark {
      font-size: 74px;
      margin-right: 8px;

      @media (orientation: portrait) {
        font-size: 66px;
      }
    }

    .intro-text {
      @media (orientation: portrait) {
        /* margin-top: 64px; */
      }
    }

    p {
      text-align: justify;
    }

    #buttons {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      padding: 4px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      width: fit-content;
      margin-inline: auto;
      display: flex;
      gap: 4px;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;

      @media (orientation: portrait) {
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 4px;
      }
    }

    #buttons a {
      border: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.45em;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      line-height: 1;
      font-size: inherit;
      color: #222;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 4px;

      * {
        transform-origin: center;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      &:hover {
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        cursor: pointer;

        * {
          transform: scale(1.05);
        }
      }

      &:active {
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);

        * {
          transform: scale(1.025);
        }
      }

      @media (orientation: portrait) {
        padding: 10px;
        font-weight: 400;
      }
    }

    #buttons a :global(.icon) {
      width: 1em;
      height: 1em;
      min-width: 1em;
      min-height: 1em;
      display: block;
    }

    a span {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    section {
      margin-top: 32px;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #222;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-family: 'Editorial Old', serif;
      font-size: 34px;
      margin: 0;

      @media (orientation: portrait) {
        margin-left: 0;
      }
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      margin-left: 0;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    li {
      line-height: 1.7em;
    }

    li:before {
      padding-right: 0.2em;
    }

    li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #222;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      padding: 1px 4px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin-right: 1px;
      cursor: pointer;

      &:hover {
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
      }
    }

    #software li:before {
      content: '✽';
    }

    #hardware li:before {
      content: '✜';
    }

    #garden li:before {
      content: '✧';
    }

    #blog li:before {
      content: '✣';
    }

    #about li:before {
      content: '✶';
    }
  </style>
</div>
